# --------------------
# Make build directory
# --------------------
#
# SYNOPSIS
# ========
#
# ::
#
#  $ Fmake_bld.sh
#
#
# DESCRIPTION
# ===========
#
#
# Under CONFIG_NAME :
# - Make the build directory 
# - Create repositories needed :
# - BLD for compilation 
#
# A tmpdir can be specified for memory issues.
#
#
# EXAMPLES
# ========
#
# ::
#
#  $ ./Fmake_bld.sh NEMOGCM/cfgs GYRE  /usr/tmp
#
#
# TODO
